summary: When I was 15 I went to comic con without any money badly wanting to meet Stan Lee. He noticed me waving in the crowd (just...
caption: When I was 15 I went to comic con without any money badly wanting to meet Stan Lee. He noticed me waving in the crowd (just wanting to be acknowledged) and sent his employee to come get me. I got a picture and autograph free of charge. He told me I was a true believer. I’ll never forget that.
